{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Everfall (1999) </strong>is a cyberpunk action game set in a dystopian world on the brink of collapse. Violent gangs, chaotic environments, and a crumbling society create a dangerous backdrop as you fight your way through hostile streets.     <br>   <br>The gameplay is simple: you run around, shoot enemies, and gather materials to unlock costumes and earn money for upgrades. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While it looks like a third-person shooter, combat uses auto-aim to lock onto the nearest enemy, with options to switch targets but no manual aiming. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The camera is fixed on the Y-axis.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you die, you lose your current loot, and you'll need to pick it up. But be careful - if you die again before reclaiming it, your lost loot will be gone for good.<br>   <br>Currently, the game features 3 levels:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A city block where you can complete quests and face enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Farm - introduces new quest mechanics and new enemies like wild boars and malfunctioning farming equipment.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A hub area where you can buy new gear and upgrade your skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The game is pretty small and basic, so please don\u2019t expect much.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>I\u2019m working on this project in my free time, and I created all the models and wrote all the code, so I\u2019m really proud of it! I hope you\u2019ll enjoy it too.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   <br><strong>More levels may be added as development progresses, but nothing is set in stone yet.</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3418300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737224070","